In Amman Airport there are different companies that provides service of car rental to all passengers. Some of the agencies offers the possibility to book
a vehicle and a driver
, it is also a good option.  Jordan sometimes can be a difficult country to have a ride if  you are not used to manage without “rules on the road”.
