공항 출국장을 나오면
핸드폰 사무실과 편의점은 왼쪽으로
은행과 렌트카 사무실들은 오른쪽으로 있음)
Tips and avices :
It is important to make sure that you can legally drive in Jordan and that you have an extra liability insurance  for your car that can cover car damage and personal injuries.
